user_query: Give me the total amounts by account type
raw_agent_output:
SELECT account_type, SUM(Amount) AS total_amount  
FROM consumption
GROUP BY account_type;

This query will return the account types and the sum of the Amount column grouped by account_type. The result will show each distinct account_type value along with the corresponding total_amount summed from the Amount column.
